function videoplay(a, b, c, d) {
    var v = document.getElementById(a);
    document.getElementById(b).style.display = 'none';
    document.getElementById(c).style.display = 'none';
    document.getElementById(d).style.display = 'none';
    v.play();
}

function Ndvideo(props) {
    const { title } = props;
    return ( <
        div className = "nd_item" >
        <
        div className = "item_video" >
        <
        video id = "video"
        preload = "auto"
        controls >
        <
        source src = "video/SƠN TÙNG M-TP - CHÚNG TA CỦA HIỆN TẠI - OFFICIAL MUSIC VIDEO.mp4" / >
        <
        /video> <
        div id = "poster"
        className = "video_poter" >
        <
        img src = "img/anhvideo.jpg"
        alt = "" / >
        <
        /div> <
        div id = "overlay"
        className = "video_overlay" / >
        <
        div id = "btn_play"
        className = "btn_play" >
        <
        button onClick = {
            () => videoplay('video', 'poster', 'overlay', 'btn_play') } >
        <
        i className = "far fa-play-circle fa-4x"
        style = {
            { color: 'white', cursor: 'pointer' } }
        /> <
        /button> <
        /div> <
        /div> <
        div className = "title_a" >
        <
        a href > { title } < /a> <
        /div> <
        div className = "item_vd_title" >
        <
        div className = "vd_title_time" >
        <
        ul >
        <
        li > VNPT < /li> <li> . </li > < li > 6 giờ trước < /li> <
        /ul> <
        /div> <
        div className = "vd_title_icon" >
        <
        span style = {
            { marginRight: 10 } } >
        <
        i className = "fab fa-youtube" / >
        <
        /span> <
        span style = {
            { marginRight: 10 } } >
        0 < i className = "far fa-thumbs-up" / >
        <
        /span> <
        span >
        0 < i className = "far fa-comment" / >
        <
        /span> <
        /div> <
        /div> <
        /div>
    );
}
export default Ndvideo;
